                        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.75" d="M4 5a1 1 0 011-1h4a1 1 0 011 1v4a1 1 0 01-1 1H5a1 1 0 01-1-1V5zM14 5a1 1 0 011-1h4a1 1 0 011 1v4a1 1 0 01-1 1h-4a1 1 0 01-1-1V5zM4 15a1 1 0 011-1h4a1 1 0 011 1v4a1 1 0 01-1 1H5a1 1 0 01-1-1v-4zM14 15a1 1 0 011-1h4a1 1 0 011 1v4a1 1 0 01-1 1h-4a1 1 0 01-1-1v-4z"/>
                    </svg>
                    <span>Dashboard</span>
